workflow.name: build_existing_model
workflow.description: Builds the OpenStudio Model for an existing building.

workflow.name: process_power_outage
workflow.description: This measures allows building power outages to be modeled. The user specifies the start time of the outage and the duration of the outage. During an outage, all energy consumption is set to 0, although occupants are still simulated in the home.

workflow.name: building_characteristics_report
workflow.description: Reports building characteristics for each simulation.

workflow.name: timeseries_csv_export
workflow.description: Exports all available hourly timeseries enduses to csv.

arguments.name: output_variables

arguments.value: Zone Mean Air Temperature, Zone Mean Radiant Temperature, Zone Indoor Air Wetbulb Temperature, Wetbulb Globe Temperature

workflow.name: server_directory_cleanup
workflow.description: Removes a significant portion of the saved results from each run, helping to alleviate memory problems.
